text: Prosopocera regia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Prosopocera regia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1936
